---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const images = [
    "/images/gymnastics-1.jpeg",
    "/images/gymnastics-2.jpeg",
    "/images/gymnastics-3.jpeg",
    "/images/gymnastics-4.jpeg",
    "/images/gymnastics-5.jpeg"
];
---

<Layout 
  title="Gymnastics - Roots N' Wings"
  description="Gymnastics at Roots N Wings Montessori promotes physical coordination, balance, and confidence, complementing the Montessori philosophy of holistic development."
  image="/images/gymnastics-1.jpeg"
>
  <NavBar />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-cover bg-center h-[400px]" style="background-image: url('/images/image6.jpg');">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Roots N' Wings Montessori School</h1>
       <p class="text-lg">
          <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a> <span class="mx-3">/</span>
          <a href="/services" class="hover:underline">Programs</a> <span class="mx-3">/</span>
          <a href="/rw" class="hover:underline">Roots N' Wings</a> <span class="mx-3">/</span>
          Gymnastics
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center max-w-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">You can do it!</h2>
           <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                Gymnastics and Montessori education share a natural alignment in promoting holistic child development.
                In Montessori environments, the emphasis on physical movement is integral to the child’s learning process,
                fostering both cognitive and motor skills. Gymnastics complements this philosophy by encouraging body
                awareness, coordination, balance, and flexibility—skills that Montessori activities also aim to
                develop through practical life exercises and sensorial materials.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Both approaches respect the child's natural rhythm and abilities, allowing them to explore their
                physical capabilities in a safe, structured environment. Just as Montessori encourages independence
                and self-directed learning, gymnastics fosters self-confidence, discipline, and resilience. By
                integrating gymnastics into Montessori programs, children can experience a well-rounded education
                that nurtures both the mind and body, helping them build a strong foundation for lifelong
                health and learning.
            </p>
      </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Carousel (Grid) -->
  <div class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-gray-800">Step n' Slide</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              {images.map(img => (
                  <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden rounded shadow-lg">
                      <img src={img} class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500" />
                  </div>
              ))}
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
